<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>镜像 on Margrop Blog</title><link>https://blog.margrop.net/en/tag/%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F/</link><description>Recent content in 镜像 on Margrop Blog</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-US</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 01 Feb 2021 15:12:47 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.margrop.net/en/tag/%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>How to Import a Third-Party VM Image into Proxmox VE</title><link>https://blog.margrop.net/en/post/pve-kvm-import-vm-format-qcow2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Feb 2021 15:12:47 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://blog.margrop.net/en/post/pve-kvm-import-vm-format-qcow2/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;In the example below, the &lt;code&gt;VM ID&lt;/code&gt; is always &lt;code&gt;100&lt;/code&gt;; change it as needed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id="file-format-conversion"&gt;File Format Conversion&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use &lt;code&gt;qemu-img&lt;/code&gt; to convert virtual disk files in other formats to &lt;code&gt;qcow2&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;For example, the following converts &lt;code&gt;vmdk&lt;/code&gt; to &lt;code&gt;qcow2&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>Upgrading or Fresh Installing MariaDB 10.5 on CentOS 7 Using Aliyun Mirror</title><link>https://blog.margrop.net/en/post/centos-7-upgrade-or-install-mariadb-10.x-aliyun-mirror/</link><pubDate>Fri, 29 Jan 2021 15:42:20 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://blog.margrop.net/en/post/centos-7-upgrade-or-install-mariadb-10.x-aliyun-mirror/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="update-the-system-first"&gt;Update the System First&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;yum update -y
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h1 id="edit-the-yum-configuration-file-using-aliyun-mirror"&gt;Edit the yum Configuration File Using Aliyun Mirror&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Here MariaDB 10.5 is used as an example&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;vim /etc/yum.repos.d/MariaDB10.repo
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;#http://downloads.mariadb.org/mariadb/repositories/&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;mariadb&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;name &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; MariaDB
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;baseurl &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; https://mirrors.aliyun.com/mariadb/yum/10.5/centos7-amd64
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;gpgkey &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; https://mirrors.aliyun.com/mariadb/yum/RPM-GPG-KEY-MariaDB
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;gpgcheck &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Installing the Latest Version of Node and NPM on CentOS 7</title><link>https://blog.margrop.net/en/post/centos-7-install-node-and-npm-latest/</link><pubDate>Wed, 27 Jan 2021 11:28:59 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://blog.margrop.net/en/post/centos-7-install-node-and-npm-latest/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="downloading-node"&gt;Downloading Node:&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The download uses the Aliyun mirror&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;mkdir ~/nodejs
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;cd ~/nodejs
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;wget https://npm.taobao.org/mirrors/node/latest-v15.x/node-v15.7.0-linux-x64.tar.gz
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;tar -xvzf node-v15.7.0-linux-x64.tar.gz
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>